buddy
------------------------------------------
A Binary Decision Diagram library, with :many highly efficient vectorized BDD
operations,dynamic variable reordering,automated garbage collection,a C++
interface with automatic reference counting,and much more.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.10-1
  libbdd-devel-2.4-1bl6
  libbdd0-2.4-1bl6
  libgcc1-14.4.0-1
  libstdc++6-14.4.0-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-3
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-14.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-14.4.0-1
  libtool-2.5.4-1
  make-4.4.1-2
  tcsh-6.24.14-1

Canonical website:
  https://sourceforge.net/projects/buddy/

Canonical download:
  mirror://sourceforge/buddy/buddy-2.4.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack buddy-2.4-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./buddy-2.4-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/buddy-2.4-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/buddy-2.4-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbdd0-2.4-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbdd-devel-2.4-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(buddy)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/buddy.README
  /usr/share/doc/buddy/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/buddy/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/buddy/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/buddy/README
  /usr/share/doc/buddy/bddnotes.ps
  /usr/share/doc/buddy/buddy.ps
  /usr/share/doc/buddy/tech.txt

(libbdd0)
  /usr/bin/cygbdd-0.dll

(libbdd-devel)
  /usr/include/buddy/bdd.h
  /usr/include/buddy/bvec.h
  /usr/include/buddy/fdd.h
  /usr/lib/libbdd.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/buddy.pc

